    "shortDescription": "<p>When you cast this spell, select a single alignment (such as lawful good or chaotic evil). Creatures of that alignment glow with a ghostly radiance while they are within your vision. Though you can see this radiance, other creatures cannot.  Spells and effects that obscure alignment, like <i>undetectable alignment</i>, also obscure the effects of this spell.</p>"
